          "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:12pt;\">Tertiary health care is generally provided in district hospitals.</span></p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 12462,
          "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:12pt;\">Sound referral system is the fundamental function.</span></p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 12463,
          "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color:black;font-size:12pt;\">Secondary level of health care constitutes the first referral unit.</span></p>"
